      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Professor Derek Santos (BSc (Hons), MSc, PhD) is a Senior Lecturer in the Dietetics, Nutrition &amp; Biological Sciences, Physiotherapy, Podiatry &amp; Radiography Division. He is also an Associate member of the Centre for Health, Activity and Rehabilitation Research.</p>]]></Value>
